= Drop us a message on mailing lists =

Before posting, please never forget about [[Netiquette]].

== Mailing lists @ ibiblio ==

* [[:List_ibiblio:sm-admin|SM-Admin]] -- **[Read Only]** A publically readable list for team member discussion.
* [[:List_ibiblio:sm-announce|SM-Announce]] -- **[Read Only]** The Source Mage GNU/Linux announce list, publically readable.
* [[:List_ibiblio:sm-commit|SM-Commit]] -- Code commit mailing list.
* [[:List_ibiblio:sm-discuss|SM-Discuss]] -- General discussion list for Source Mage GNU/Linux. Meant to mirror **SM-Admin** for non-team members (non-technical).
* [[:List_ibiblio:sm-grimoire-bugs|SM-Grimoire-Bugs]] -- **[Read Only]** list for grimoire bugs that need a wider audience of distribution, possibly for wider discussion.
* [[:List_ibiblio:sm-security|SM-Security]] -- Discuss Source Mage GNU/Linux security issues and keep watch on [[Security format|security bugs]].
* [[:List_ibiblio:sm-spell-submit|SM-Spell-Submit]] -- A moderated list for receiving announcements about updated software from [[http://sourceforge.net|SourceForge]] and other sources.
* [[:List_ibiblio:sm-users|SM-Users]] -- General discussion list for Source Mage GNU/Linux. A question and answer list (technical).